    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Provide technical and logistics support to AMRMSC and NTWCConduct need assessments and improve infrastructure for human and animal health laboratories Conduct capacity building activities for human health, animal health and food sectors labsSupport to strengthen laboratory quality assurance and biosafety and waste managementStrengthen capacity of NPHL as National Reference Lab (NRL) for HH and National Coordinating Center (NCC) and CVL as NRL for AH for AMR Improve AMR data management at NCC and site levelFoster regular interaction among laboratory professionals and clinicians, diagnostic and antimicrobial stewardshipAMR data sharing and use to promote rational prescription, update treatment guidelinesConduct AMU survey at 12 sites and disseminate survey findingsSupport CVL in conducting active surveillance in 4 surveillance sites Conduct need assessment of DFTQC lab and support to strengthen infrastructureConduct situation analysis and feasibility assessment for AMR surveillance in environment sectorTechnical and logistic support to DDA for AMC related activities Support VSDRL on equipment and software upgrades and on-site technical support in data management and reporting of AMC/AMU data to OIE"
    },
